ase="F59337804" href="IFRS17_59.dita#IFRS17_59" id="IFRS17_X0437">59(b)</xref>; and</p>       </li><li id="IFRS17_97_c"><li_value>(c)</li_value>         <p base="F55666665" id="IFRS17_P0384">the method it has chosen to recognise&#xa0;insurance acquisition cash flows&#xa0;applying&#xa0;<xref base="F59235396" href="IFRS17_59.dita#IFRS17_59" id="IFRS17_X0438">paragraph&#xa0;59(a)</xref>.</p>       </li></ol></bodydiv></body></paragraph>